Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.65,ED_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}吸って息をして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:33.45,ED_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}笑ったり泣いたりして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:39.18,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}気づいてよ  嘘の優しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.55,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}見て見ぬフリした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:45.55,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}ひとり雨宿り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:49.10,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}けど 空に罪はない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.55,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}ワタシだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.75,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}もっている花言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:59.10,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}見失い また夢中で探した
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:03.16,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}他の誰かじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:04.95,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}見つけられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:07.79,ED_JP4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}大事なモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:12.20,ED_JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}昨日のワタシと  交わした約束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:16.71,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}思い出し  また明日を探した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:20.72,ED_JP1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}花びらが散らぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:25.55,ED_JP1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}私は私を抱きしめるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:19.80,ED_CHT1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}过于耀眼的太阳阴影下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:24.04,ED_CHT1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我是无人察觉散发芬芳的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.25,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我竭力地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.65,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}汲取水分呼吸着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:33.45,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}时而会欢笑时而会哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:39.18,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}请注意到我  装作不曾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.55,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}看到温柔的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:45.55,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}独自在躲雨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:49.10,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}但是 天空并无罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.55,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}将属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.75,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}一个人的花语给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:59.10,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}迷失了 然后便不顾一切找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:03.16,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}这是任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:04.95,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}都无法发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:07.79,ED_CHT4,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}都无法发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:12.20,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我由此想起了和昨天的自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:16.71,ED_CHT3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}那个约定  明天再次去找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:20.72,ED_CHT1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}为了不让花瓣飘散凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:25.55,ED_CHT1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我就此紧紧地拥着自己
